```plantuml
@startuml RunnersHi_RunnersHi_Server

actor User
participant "Client App" as Client
participant "Express Server" as Server
participant "Socket.IO" as Socket
participant "Auth Middleware" as Auth
participant "User Controller" as UserCtrl
participant "User Model" as UserModel
participant "Matching Controller" as MatchCtrl
participant "Matching Model" as MatchModel
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Client: Login/Register
Client -> Server: POST /api/auth/login
Server -> Auth: Verify credentials
Auth -> UserCtrl: Handle authentication
UserCtrl -> UserModel: Query user data
UserModel -> DB: SELECT user
DB --> UserModel: User data
UserModel --> UserCtrl: User object
UserCtrl --> Auth: Auth response
Auth --> Server: JWT token
Server --> Client: Auth response with token

User -> Client: Request matching
Client -> Socket: Emit 'findMatch' event
Socket -> MatchCtrl: Handle match request
MatchCtrl -> MatchModel: Find suitable opponent
MatchModel -> DB: Query available runners
DB --> MatchModel: Runner data
MatchModel --> MatchCtrl: Match result
MatchCtrl -> Socket: Emit 'matchFound' event
Socket --> Client: Notify match found

User -> Client: Start running
Client -> Socket: Emit 'startRunning' event
Socket -> MatchCtrl: Handle running start
MatchCtrl -> MatchModel: Create running session
MatchModel -> DB: INSERT running data
DB --> MatchModel: Session ID
MatchModel --> MatchCtrl: Session confirmation
MatchCtrl -> Socket: Emit 'runningStarted' event
Socket --> Client: Confirm running started

User -> Client: Send location updates
Client -> Socket: Emit 'locationUpdate' event
Socket -> MatchCtrl: Handle location update
MatchCtrl -> MatchModel: Store coordinates
MatchModel -> DB: UPDATE session data
DB --> MatchModel: Update confirmation
MatchModel --> MatchCtrl: Update status
MatchCtrl -> Socket: Emit 'opponentUpdate' event
Socket --> Client: Update opponent position

User -> Client: Finish running
Client -> Socket: Emit 'finishRun' event
Socket -> MatchCtrl: Handle run completion
MatchCtrl -> MatchModel: Finalize session
MatchModel -> DB: UPDATE results
DB --> MatchModel: Completion status
MatchModel --> MatchCtrl: Run summary
MatchCtrl -> Socket: Emit 'runCompleted' event
Socket --> Client: Send final results

@enduml
```